px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0508c82d4bd07bd18a081031a2b9dd03/eafa0/flex5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.77215189873418%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Untitled\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/0508c82d4bd07bd18a081031a2b9dd03/f058b/flex5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0508c82d4bd07bd18a081031a2b9dd03/c26ae/flex5.png 158w,\n/static/0508c82d4bd07bd18a081031a2b9dd03/6bdcf/flex5.png 315w,\n/static/0508c82d4bd07bd18a081031a2b9dd03/f058b/flex5.png 630w,\n/static/0508c82d4bd07bd18a081031a2b9dd03/eafa0/flex5.png 939w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>align-self는 부모 요소와 관계 없이 아이템 하나를 개별적으로 정렬하고 싶을 때 사용한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2606ef0cf138bfcc130dd15abd82bd68/0940f/flex6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.49367088607595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Untitled\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/2606ef0cf138bfcc130dd15abd82bd68/f058b/flex6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2606ef0cf138bfcc130dd15abd82bd68/c26ae/flex6.png 158w,\n/static/2606ef0cf138bfcc130dd15abd82bd68/6bdcf/flex6.png 315w,\n/static/2606ef0cf138bfcc130dd15abd82bd68/f058b/flex6.png 630w,\n/static/2606ef0cf138bfcc130dd15abd82bd68/40601/flex6.png 945w,\n/static/2606ef0cf138bfcc130dd15abd82bd68/0940f/flex6.png 1154w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>flex-grow, flex-shrink, flex-basis</h1>\n<p>이 속성들도 개별 아이템 하나에 적용하는 속성이다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>flex-basis\n<ul>\n<li>flex 아이템의 기본 크기</li>\n<li>flex-direction이 row면 width, column이면 height</li>\n<li>flex-basis를 0으로 지정하면 아이템이 점유하는 공간을 0으로 여겨 모든 공간을 여백으로 간주한다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>flex-grow\n<ul>\n<li>flex 컨테이너가 아이템들의 너비보다 클 때, 남은 여백을 채우는 데 각 아이템이 몇의 비율로 채울 지 정하는 속성</li>\n<li>아래 예제에서는 1:2:1의 비율로 여백을 채움</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b18f1991f3745fc7ce55fba94776052d/75a80/flex7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.39240506329114%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: bl